                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17521206-2-victim36 t17521206-2-viclabel9"></join>; I lost two chariot harnesses out of my shop on the 25th of Sept. having seen them that day, I advertised them on the 29th, and on that day I saw one of them on a horse in a hackney-coach going by, belonging to 
               <persName id="t17521206-2-person38">
                  William 
                  Flin 
               <interp inst="t17521206-2-person38" type="surname" value="Flin"></interp>
